name: getEventInsights
description: Gets a set of Event-specific insights for the given Event.

If-None-Match.description: Value of the `ETag` header in the most recently cached response by the client.

$block: A year-specific event insight object expressed as a JSON string, separated in to `qual` and `playoff` fields. See also Event_Insights_2016, Event_Insights_2017, etc.

$ul: **playoff**: Insights for the playoff round of an event
**qual**: Inights for the qualification round of an event
